item.title: CVE-2021-24134|2024-08-03T19:21:18.263Z -- unknown -- constant%20contact%20forms
item.description: Unvalidated input and lack of output encoding in the Constant Contact Forms WordPress plugin, versions before 1.8.8, lead to multiple Stored Cross-Site Scripting vulnerabilities, which allowed high-privileged user (Editor+) to inject arbitrary JavaScript code or HTML in posts where the malicious form is embed.
